    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited as a project car or for parts. The exterior shows significant wear, including noticeable rust patches on the rocker panels and several large dents. Mechanically, the engine runs but has a persistent knock and the transmission shifts harshly. The interior has seen better days, with torn upholstery and some non-functional electronics. It will require a trailer for transport as it is not currently roadworthy, but it offers a solid foundation for someone with the time and tools for a full restoration.",
