    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly a showroom-quality find for the discerning collector or enthusiast. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, free of any chips, scratches, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine state, with the leather upholstery still smelling fresh and showing no signs of wear or creasing. Every mechanical component has been meticulously maintained, ensuring a driving experience that feels as crisp and responsive as the day it first left the dealership.",
      "price": 48500.0,
