    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a refined example of automotive engineering, this vehicle has been maintained to a high standard, ensuring both mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal. It offers a sophisticated driving experience, characterized by reliable performance and a well-preserved interior. This selection represents a premier opportunity for the discerning buyer seeking a balance of luxury and proven longevity. We invite you to experience the quality and poise of this exceptional offering.",
      "price": 34500.0,
